<view class='detail'>
<!-- 视频图片都存在 -->
<view class="swiper">
<view wx:if="{{detailData.imgArr.length>=1 && detailData.videoArr!==''}}"> 
  <view wx:if="{{imgArrShow}}">
      <swiper class="detail-image" indicator-dots="{{indicatorDots}}" bindchange="swiperChange" autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" duration="{{duration}}" circular="{{circular}}">
      <block wx:for="{{detailData.imgArr}}" wx:key="imgArr">
        <swiper-item  bindtap="handlePrevewImage" data-url="{{item}}">
          <image class="slide-image" src="{{item}}"></image>
        </swiper-item>
      </block>
    </swiper>
    <view class="indexShow">
      <text style="font-size: 28rpx">{{swiperIndex}}</text>
      <text style="font-size: 24rpx">/</text>
      <text style="font-size: 24rpx">{{detailData.imgArr.length}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view> 
</view>

    <view class='detail-cont'>
      <view class='detail-title' >￥{{detailData.GoodsPrice}}</view>
      <view class='detail-title1'>已售 {{detailData.GoodsSale}}件</view>
      <view class='detail-title2'>  【山大文创】{{detailData.GoodsName}}</view>

         <!-- <van-cell style="background-color: red;"  title="规格" value="<请选择数量、颜色>" bind:click="tobuy1" /> -->
      </view>

      <view style="width: 100%;height: 250px;background-color: #F8F8F8; position: absolute;top: 370px;">
         <view style="width: 100%;height: 50px; margin:10px auto;background-color: #FFFFFF;line-height: 50px;">
         <view style="float: left; color: rgb(134, 134, 134);font-size: 12px;margin: 0 16px;">规格</view>
         <view style="float: left;font-size: 12px;" bindtap='tobuy1'>{{guige}}</view>
         </view>

         <view style="width: 100%;height: 50px; margin:10px auto;background-color: #FFFFFF;line-height: 50px;">
         <view style="float: left; color: rgb(134, 134, 134);font-size: 12px;margin: 0 16px;">配送</view>
         <view style="float: left;font-size: 12px;"><van-icon name="passed" /> 商家配送</view>
         <view style="float: left;font-size: 12px;margin-left: 5px;"><van-icon name="passed" /> 到店自取</view>
         </view>
         <van-divider contentPosition="center">详情介绍</van-divider>
         <van-image
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          lazy-load
          src="https://img.yzcdn.cn/vant/cat.jpeg"
        />
     </view>
          
    <view class='detail-bottom'>
      <van-goods-action>
      <van-goods-action-icon icon="wap-home-o" bindtap="gohome" text="主页" />
      <van-goods-action-icon icon="cart-o" bindtap="gocart" text="购物车" info="{{carslen}}" />
      <van-goods-action-button color="#00cccc" bindtap='tobuy1'  text="加入购物车" type="warning" />
      <van-goods-action-button color="#009494" bindtap="tobuy" text="立即购买" />
    </van-goods-action>
      <!-- <view class='addCart' bindtap='tobuy1'>加入购物车</view>
      <van-button class='buyNow' bindtap="tobuy"  type="danger" block>立即购买</van-button> -->

    </view>
</view>


<!-- 购买数量 -->
<van-popup show="{{show}}" bind:close="onClose" round closeable position="bottom"
  custom-style="padding-top:25rpx;max-height: 80%;" >
  <van-card centered price="{{ detailData.GoodsPrice }}"
    desc="库存 {{detailData.GoodsNum}} 件"
    title="【山大文创】{{ detailData.GoodsName }}" thumb="{{detailData.imgArr[0]}}" />
  <van-cell title="购买数量">
    <view>
      <van-stepper value="{{ buyNumber }}" min="{{ buyNumMin }}" max="{{ buyNumMax }}" bind:change="stepChange" />
    </view>
  </van-cell>
  <van-button wx:if="{{flag}}" class="buyNow1" bindtap="nowBuy"  type="danger" block>立即购买</van-button>
  <van-button wx:else class="buyNow2" bindtap="addMyCart"  type="danger" block>加入购物车</van-button>
</van-popup>